Description:
   Measured Response is a passive combat philosophy mastered by senior
   Sentinels. Rather than reacting emotionally or instinctively to attacks,
   the Sentinel evaluates each incoming strike and responds with calculated
   precision. This discipline reduces the Sentinel's susceptibility to
   feints and distractions while improving counter-attack timing.

   The passive benefit of Measured Response improves the Sentinel's ability
   to land retaliatory attacks after successfully defending. When the Sentinel
   blocks, parries, or evades an incoming blow, Measured Response triggers
   a follow-up counter-attack at improved accuracy. The skill embodies the
   Sentinel doctrine that every defensive action should create an offensive
   opportunity.
